FeedPackage.Description:
A flexible auto-registration module that extends Simple Injector Inversion of Control IoC container (https://simpleinjector.org).
By default, this will register the basic types with simple registrations, including more complex generics. It also adds support for your IEnumerable<>, Lazy<>, and Func<> dependencies.
Optionally, you can configure this to automatically register your decorators and you can extend or supercede it with your own custom auto-registration providers.
Feel free to review the code or submit pull requests through GitHub.

FeedPackage.Description:
SocketIO4Net.Client is a C# websocket client for the very popular Socket.IO project by Guillermo Rauch. It leverages the WebSocket4Net client and SuperWebSocket library by Kerry Jiang as the underlying websocket provider.
SocketIO4Net.Client can interact with Socket.IO instances in a very similar manner as Socket.IO JavaScript clients. This project aims to fill the JavaScript client and C# client gap for Socket.IO, and retain a very similar application experience.
FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes:
This version only works with the Socket.IO 'websocket' transport layer. Secure Sockets (https / wss) are not supported.
It is compatible with websocket drafts: Hybi-00, Hybi-10, RFC6455
FeedPackage.Summary: .net 4.0 websocket client for Socket.IO
FeedPackage.Title: SocketIO4Net.Client
